Decentralized Healthcare Data Exchange
A blockchain-based healthcare data exchange using XRPL and IPFS

Overview
This project is a decentralized healthcare data exchange built on the XRPL blockchain and IPFS (InterPlanetary File System). It allows secure storage, retrieval, and exchange of healthcare data while ensuring privacy, transparency, and security.

Tech Stack
Frontend: React.js

Backend: Node.js, Express.js

Blockchain: XRPL (XRP Ledger)

Storage: IPFS

Database: (If needed, mention MySQL, MongoDB, etc.)

Project Structure
xrpl-healthcare/
